# CodedPixels Code Standards

Stack: **Next.js 15 App Router**, **TypeScript strict**, **Tailwind 4.x**, **Lucide** icons, **Inter** font (`docs/brand/brand-guide.md` tokens).

## Money (ENG-004)

- All amounts in **integer pence** — no floats in totals
- Annual recurring only: `Math.round(monthlyTotalPence * 12 * 83 / 100)` — multiply in this exact order
- One-time £149 → separate `oneTimeFeesPence` (14900), not in `monthlyTotalPence`
- Live configurator total is authoritative; package card prices are marketing labels

## Config state (ENG-006)

- URL params: `template`, `features`, `billing`, `customTemplate`, `package`
- Invalid params → partial restore per Q40; round-trip tests required before Wave 3 UI

## Security

- No client writes to `signups`, `waitlist_site_import`, or tenant data
- M3+: Callable Functions + App Check; rules from `docs/specs/firestore-rules-spec.md` §11
- Sentry with PII scrubbing before any PII endpoint ships (INF-004)

## UI / brand

- Tokens: primary `#4F46E5`, accent `#06B6D4`, success `#10B981`, bg `#FAFAFA`, dark `#0F172A`
- Live price: accent colour + `aria-live="polite"`
- Toggles: `role="switch"`, `aria-checked`; contrast ≥ 4.5:1 (Dr. Nadia Sokolov)

## Quality before PR (Nathan wave close)

```bash
npm run lint && npm run typecheck && npm test && npm run build
```

**All tests must pass** — full suite, zero failures. Firestore changes: `npm run test:rules` must also pass. **No commit/push otherwise.**
